						<summary>

						<p>This is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Siddhārthi, Āśvīja, śu. 10,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1439 September 18, Friday</hi> (not verifiable), in the reign of <hi rend="bold">Dēvarāya-Mahārāya.</hi> It records that the king's servant <hi rend="bold">Kaṭigeya Āhamuda-Khāna</hi> caused the construction of a rest-house and a well, for the merit of the king.</p>						

